<P>
   MET-NETHERLANDISH-EXHIBIT (New York) _ Welcome to heaven. Or
more accurately, to heaven on earth. That's the terrain mapped out
in crisp, luminous detail in ``From van Eyck to Bruegel: Early
Netherlandish Painting in the Metropolitan Museum of Art.'' By
Holland Cotter.
</P>
<P>
   NY-BOOK-COUNTRY (New York) _ Life and literature intertwined in
a city that speaks volumes. By Grace Paley.
</P>
