<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-25 01:30 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3682 &Cx1f; tic-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FBC-ASU-GREEN-AZR &LR;      09-25 0736
