<P>
   FLU _ The flu shot just got easier to take _ testing of the
first oral flu pill has been completed and the results are good.
Hoffman LaRoche's pill significantly reduces the incidence of
influenza and works in treating it, too, reducing the duration of
illness and the severity of symptoms. The company made the
announcement Friday during the Interscience Conference on
Antimicrobial Agents and Chemotherapy in San Diego. (Kim, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) ETA: 5 p.m.
