of Bible Code Revealed, based on a book that claims the Bible
includes buried information on events of the past, present and
future. The West Palm Beach, Florida-based network, which parent
Paxson Communications (AMEX: PAX, $9.75) launched last month, will
air the two-hour special from 8 p.m. to 10 p.m. Oct. 30, according
to Paxson. (Plunkett, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
