team for SMU, coached by former Georgia assistant Mike Cavan. The
Mustangs lost to Arkansas 44-17 in Little Rock last week. ...
Mississippi running back Joe Gunn rushed for 146 yards, the most by
a Ole Miss freshman in 10 years, in last week's 30-6 victory at
Vanderbilt.
