a new school record with a victory over the Wildcats, who haven't
won at Florida Field since 1979. ... Kentucky's Tim Couch has
passed for 1,171 yards and 13 touchdowns in leading the Wildcats to
their best start in 14 years. ... Florida has not lost back-to-back
