the series, winning both games by one point at Bryant-Denny Stadium
in Tuscaloosa. ... Chrys Chukwuma rushed for a career-high 142
yards in Arkansas' 44-17 victory over SMU last week. ... Alabama
had a week off after opening the season with home victories over
