</P>
<P>
   -- Game notes: After playing nationally ranked teams in its
first two games, the Volunteers appear to receive a break this week
against a winless Houston squad outscored 70-41 in its three
losses. ... Tennessee officials had to replace an estimated $25,000
worth of damages at Neyland Stadium caused by fans celebrating last
