<P>
   RUSSIA-OLIGARCHS (Moscow) _ It's the Autumn of the Oligarchs in
Russia, as crony capitalism gives way to some sort of quasi return
to a more state controlled economy. But Victor Potanin, 37, the
head of one of Russia's rangiest business-banking-media combines,
is hardly in full scale retreat. By Timothy L. O'Brien. &UR;  &LR; (Moved).
